text: Francisco Guterres, popularly known as Lú-Olo (born 7 September 1954Profile on National Parliament website) is an East Timorese politician. He was the 6th President of East Timor from 2017 to 2022. He lost re-election to former President José Ramos-Horta in 2022. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of East Timor
